_aLatestUpdates._sText: Made the installation instructions inside the readme.txt file more clear.

_sName: Place Painted NAV File for Map DE_AIRSTRIP_CSS
_sText:
This is a NAV file for the remake of the CS 1.6 map de_airstrip  kindly created by Aynekko.  You can find it here: MAP

Probably needless to say that the NAV file will work with only that version of the map, no matter how many remakes are out there.

As usual it is fully place named according to the original map, so that you can have a great time on this with Bots, as they'll be using the radio properly.

Enjoy!
